Package: IQSSdevtools
Title: Initialize and Compile Packages Complying with IQSS Best Practices for 
    Software Development and Sustainability
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Gandrud", email = "zelig.zee@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    person("Institute for Quantitative Social Science", "Harvard University"), 
    role = "cph")
Description: The IQSSdevtools package makes it easy to initialize and compile an 
    R software package that complies with the IQSS Best Practices for Software 
    Development and Sustainability (IBPSDS).
